blueprint Robot (id_number, name, model_number):

@:has
  id: id_number.substring(3),
  name: name,
  model_no: model_number,
  hp: 100,
  mana: 80

@:does
  regen: proc ():
    @hp++
  ..,
  login: fn ():
    return @id == "3000"
  ..
  
@:syn:get
  name: proc (): return @name ..,
  model_no: proc (): return @model_no ..

@:syn:set
  mana: fn (new_mana):
    @mana = new_mana
  ..,
  newID: proc ():
    @id = "3000"
    set.mana(75)
  ..

defcc

==========

$ robot = construct Robot(name="Miles")

>>Analyses to:

$ robot = construct Robot(undefined, "Miles", undefined)